<br>
The entire shaman and enchanter lines check vs magic to see if they land.  They are curable by Cure Disease, but they don't check your DR first.  The slows that are DR are the one in FG from the shrooms and Bane of Thule in CT, which is currently basically unresistable anyway.<br>
<br>
It's a common misconception actually..people think if it gets cured by cure disease that it checks vs disease.  That's not exactly how it works.  Tash is curable by cure poison too, but doesn't check your PR. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=48986">Haass Wolvesbane</a> <BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=71943">Cagna Soulshaker</a> 

